    <b>Strategic Highlights & Annotations:</b>
    <ul style="font-size:13px; line-height:1.4;">
      <li><b>Risk Buffers:</b> for evaluation & integration phases to account for failed experiments or dataset limitations.</li>
      <li><b>Parallel Tracks:</b> Continuous monitoring of research & publications(runs across all 3 years to stay updated on latest findings.</li>
      <li><b>Critical Path in orange:</b> Sequential dependencies: Literature → Problem → Design → Prototype → Evaluation → Publication.</li>
      <li><b>Safe Overlaps:</b> Experiments and monitoring tasks overlap strategically to reduce idle periods and optimize timeline efficiency.</li>
      <li><b>Continuous Research Monitoring:</b> Ensures my thesis remains aligned with evolving Q1/Q2-level research and avoids obsolescence.</li>
      
    </ul>
	
